{"tid":984934,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日,我悟了“欲愛是苦”。","createTime":"2019-01-17T07:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T07:56:10.000Z","uid":140357,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b3f15c71534c119539e4187d7633e64decee673","tid":984934,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:56:10.000Z","msg":"佛陀說：「因愛而生憂，因愛而生懼；無愛亦無憂，無愛亦無懼。」<br />\n<br />\n原來不再追求男女之情,放下貪嗔痴。人生再無苦,大自在也。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.charity.idv.tw/1/a41.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.charity.idv.tw%2F1%2Fa41.html&d=b1OF%2B0C98ImIiU9%2BlqVqRtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d93de066\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.charity.idv.tw/1/a41.html</a>"}]}